pve-xpu-manager (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Intel GPU discovery and identification (Flex, PVC, BMG)
  * Real-time telemetry (temperature, power, memory)
  * SR-IOV virtual function management (create, list, inspect, remove)
  * Boot persistence via systemd service
  * Proxmox web UI integration as native node tab
  * Compatible with PVE 8.x and 9.x

 -- PVE XPU Manager <pve-xpu@localhost>  Sat, 22 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
